2. Key Technical Concepts:
   - TDD red-green-refactor cycle (hybrid v6: skills in main context, refactor as subagent)
   - TypeScript with strict types (Item, Customer, Step, Scenario)
   - Vitest (`it.todo`, `it`, `describe`, `expect`)
